@RNanwani 

You will need to upgrade truffle to a version that supports the constructor syntax. It became possible with solc `0.4.23` and [truffle 4.1.7](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/releases/tag/v4.1.7).

 I don't understand how you're getting 4.0.4 from the instructions suggested above - the current release is `4.1.12`
